      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Please do not make any changes to your warfarin regimen without consulting your healthcare provider. While some natural foods can affect blood clotting, abruptly stopping a prescribed anticoagulant is extremely dangerous and could lead to a stroke or blood clots. You must discuss any dietary or supplement changes with your doctor to safely manage your INR levels.",
